                  </hi>. I am clerk to Mr. Cohen, ship-chandler, at Rat<lb></lb>cliff. On 27th June the prisoner came, and said he wanted some new</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185007080106"></xptr>
               <p>rigging, and asked if we would buy any old—he represented himself as captain of the <hi rend="italic">Isabella</hi>—the first lot he brought we gave him 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a cwt. for.</p>
